 des approches multi-échelles intégrant les aspects produit/procédé.  aMode of access: Internet via World Wide Web.  aIn French.0 aDescription based on online resource; title from PDF title page (publisher's Web site, viewed 24. Apr 2022) 4aNutrition. 7aMEDICAL / Nutrition.2bisacsh1 aAxelos, Monique, econtributor.4ctb4https://id.loc.gov/vocabulary/relators/ctb1 aBakalis, Serafim, econtributor.4ctb4https://id.loc.gov/vocabulary/relators/ctb1 aCanselier, Jean-Paul, eauthor.4aut4http://id.loc.gov/vocabulary/relators/aut1 aChanlot, Gaëlle, econtributor.4ctb4https://id.loc.gov/vocabulary/relators/ctb1 aCuvelier, Gérard, econtributor.4ctb4https://id.loc.gov/vocabulary/relators/ctb1 aDe Broucker, Thibault, econtributor.4ctb4https://id.loc.gov/vocabulary/relators/ctb1 aDucept, Fabrice, econtributor.4ctb4https://id.loc.gov/vocabulary/relators/ctb1 aDulauroy, Magali, econtributor.4ctb4https://id.loc.gov/vocabulary/relators/ctb1 aDupont, Didier, econtributor.4ctb4https://id.loc.gov/vocabulary/relators/ctb1 aFryer, Peter, econtributor.4ctb4https://id.loc.gov/vocabulary/relators/ctb1 aGreenwood, Richard, econtributor.4ctb4https://id.loc.gov/vocabulary/relators/ctb1 aLe Breton, Laurent, econtributor.4ctb4https://id.loc.gov/vocabulary/relators/ctb1 aLoubens, Clément de, econtributor.4ctb4https://id.loc.gov/vocabulary/relators/ctb1 aMichon, Camille, econtributor.4ctb4https://id.loc.gov/vocabulary/relators/ctb1 aPascal, Gérard, econtributor.4ctb4https://id.loc.gov/vocabulary/relators/ctb1 aRutledge, Douglas N., econtributor.4ctb4https://id.loc.gov/vocabulary/relators/ctb1 aSieffermann, Jean-Marc, econtributor.4ctb4https://id.loc.gov/vocabulary/relators/ctb1 aSoler, Louis George, econtributor.4ctb4https://id.loc.gov/vocabulary/relators/ctb1 aSouchon, Isabelle, econtributor.4ctb4https://id.loc.gov/vocabulary/relators/ctb1 aSoulier, Jean-Marie, econtributor.4ctb4https://id.loc